What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Non Thermal Pasteurization Market?

Market Analysis and Size

The expansion of the convenience food sector, which includes products such as frozen foods and ready-to-eat foods, has increased demand for non-thermal pasteurization, as these technologies reduce processing time and increase production capacity to meet market demand.

